      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARD COUNTER (1) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 270m behind Youarethereason (16.75) in a D2. Rates on top in this line up. MAKEIT JACKSON (3) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (27.41) at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Must be included in calculations. STRATTON GIRL (2) missed the frame two runs back then won at her latest appearance by 2.75 lengths at this track over 270m (16.06). Up a notch here but latest effort enough to test this field. UNKNOWN FEVER (5) is racing very well, claiming a D4 two back then scored a one length win of a D3 at this track over 270m (16.33) last time. Goes up another notch but will give backers a sight.",
